---
Portable memory layer for AI coding agents

Usage: dreamd [COMMAND]

Commands:
  doctor   Run health checks and print status (dream-cycle mode, etc.)
  dream    Run the deterministic dream cycle: promote top cluster to LESSONS.md, prune decayed episodic events
  init     Scaffold per-project .agent/ store and register it with the daemon
  mcp      Start the MCP server (bridges to daemon if running, otherwise in-process)
  reset    Reset scratch state (DR-113). Today only `workspace` is supported
  version  Print structured version information (semver, commit, build date, target, schema)
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -V, --version
          Print version information

  -h, --help
          Print help
